{"case_id": "complex_001", "category": "复杂条件理解", "title": "双人值班组合", "model_name": "mock/mock-model-v1", "provider_type": "mock", "is_mock": true, "prompt_version": "optimized", "input": "某团队要从甲、乙、丙、丁中选两人值班。条件：甲入选则乙不能入选；丙入选则丁必须入选；乙和丁至少一人入选；甲本周请假不能入选。请给出所有可行组合并简述判断。", "output": "甲因请假被排除；乙和丙违反丙必须与丁同组。可行组合仅为乙和丁、丙和丁。", "latency_ms": 0.021, "status": "success", "error_message": "", "created_at": "2026-06-20T12:46:35.753195+00:00", "risk_level": "low", "expected_format": "中文文本", "rule_passed": true, "rule_score": 1.0, "failed_rules": [], "badcase_category": "none", "rule_checks": [{"rule": "max_chars", "passed": true, "detail": "实际 35，上限 160"}, {"rule": "required_keywords_all", "passed": true, "detail": "关键词完整"}]}
